{"title_page": "Deepu Karunakaran", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2016}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=September 2016}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name          = Deepu Karunakaran\n| birth_place   = [[Trivandrum]], [[Kerala]], India\n| residence     = Trivandrum\n| birth_date    = {{birth-date and age|13 July 1977}}\n| occupation    = Film director\n|spouse         = Archana Mohan (2015\u2013present)\n}}\n\n'''Deepu Karunakaran''' is an Indian film director who works in [[Malayalam cinema]]. He debuted in direction with movie \"Winter\", as the release was late due to many reasons, his first movie came in theatre was in 2008 with the [[Dileep (actor)|Dileep]] starrer ''[[Crazy Gopalan]]''.\n\n==Career==\n\nPrior to becoming an independent filmmaker, Deepu apprenticed as an assistant director under [[Priyadarshan]]. His first released film was in 2008, ''[[Crazy Gopalan]]''. Though he made film \"Winter\" in which [[Jayaram]] acted and later with [[Prithviraj Sukumaran|Prithviraj]] in the lead. He directed [[Mammootty]] in the 2015 thriller ''[[Fireman]]'', which was a success critically and commercially.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news/Mammootty-worked-continuously-for-30-nights-for-Fireman-Deepu-Karunakaran/articleshow/45522738.cms | title=Mammootty worked continuously for 30 nights for Fireman: Deepu Karunakaran | work=timesofindia.indiatimes.com | accessdate=7 May 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.khaleejtimes.com/citytimes/bollywood/fiery-success-with-deepu-karunakaran-s-fireman | title=Fiery success with Deepu Karunakaran\u2019s Fireman | work=khaleejtimes.com | accessdate=7 May 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Personal life==\n\nDeepu Karunakaran is married to Archana Mohan. The couple were married in [[Trivandrum]] on 17 January 2015.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/events/kochi/Suchithra-spotted-in-her-ethnic-best-at-Deepu-Karunakarans-wedding-in-Trivandrum/articleshow/45922731.cms | title=Suchithra spotted in her ethnic best at Deepu Karunakaran's wedding in Trivandrum | work=timesofindia.indiatimes.com | accessdate=7 May 2016}}</ref> He is also the brother of actress [[Suchitra Murali]].\n\n==Filmography==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" \n|-\n!No !! Year !! Film !! Role !!Cast || Notes\n|-\n|1|| 2008|| ''[[Crazy Gopalan]]'' || Director<br>Writer ||[[Dileep (actor)|Dileep]], [[Saleem Kumar]], [[Manoj K. Jayan]], Radha Varma ||\n|-\n|2|| 2009 || ''[[Winter (2009 film)|Winter]]'' || Director || [[Jayaram]], [[Bhavana (actress)|Bhavana]] ||\n|-\n|3|| 2011 || ''[[Teja Bhai & Family]]'' || Director || [[Prithviraj Sukumaran|Prithviraj]], [[Akhila Sasidharan|Akhila]] ||\n|-\n|4|| 2015 || ''[[Fireman (film)|Fireman]]'' || Director || [[Mammootty]], [[Nyla Usha]] ||\n|-\n|5|| 2016 || ''[[Karinkunnam 6S]]'' || Director || [[Manju Warrier]], [[Anoop Menon]] ||<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nowrunning.com/karingunnam-sixes-shoot-completed/119772/story.htm | title='Karingunnam Sixes' shoot completed | work=nowrunning.com | accessdate=7 May 2016}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n*{{IMDb name|nm3254695}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Karunakaran, Deepu}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Film directors from Thiruvananthapuram]]\n[[Category:Malayalam film directors]]\n[[Category:21st-century Indian film directors]]\n[[Category:1977 births]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2016}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=September 2016}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name          = Deepu Karunakaran\n| birth_place   = [[Trivandrum]], [[Kerala]], India\n| residence     = Trivandrum\n| birth_date    = {{birth-date and age|13 July 1977}}\n| occupation    = Film director\n|spouse         = Archana Mohan (2015-present)\n}}\n\n'''Deepu Karunakaran''' is an Indian film director who works in [[Malayalam cinema]]. He debuted in direction with movie \"Winter\", as the release was late due to many reasons, his first movie came in theatre was in 2008 with the [[Dileep (actor)|Dileep]] starrer ''[[Crazy Gopalan]]''.\n\n==Career==\n\nPrior to becoming an independent filmmaker, Deepu apprenticed as an assistant director under [[Priyadarshan]]. His first released film was in 2008, ''[[Crazy Gopalan]]''. Though he made film \"Winter\" in which [[Jayaram]] acted and later with [[Prithviraj Sukumaran|Prithviraj]] in the lead. He directed [[Mammootty]] in the 2015 thriller ''[[Fireman]]'', which was a success critically and commercially.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news/Mammootty-worked-continuously-for-30-nights-for-Fireman-Deepu-Karunakaran/articleshow/45522738.cms | title=Mammootty worked continuously for 30 nights for Fireman: Deepu Karunakaran | work=timesofindia.indiatimes.com | accessdate=7 May 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.khaleejtimes.com/citytimes/bollywood/fiery-success-with-deepu-karunakaran-s-fireman | title=Fiery success with Deepu Karunakaran\u2019s Fireman | work=khaleejtimes.com | accessdate=7 May 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Personal life==\n\nDeepu Karunakaran is married to Archana Mohan. The couple were married in [[Trivandrum]] on 17 January 2015.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/events/kochi/Suchithra-spotted-in-her-ethnic-best-at-Deepu-Karunakarans-wedding-in-Trivandrum/articleshow/45922731.cms | title=Suchithra spotted in her ethnic best at Deepu Karunakaran's wedding in Trivandrum | work=timesofindia.indiatimes.com | accessdate=7 May 2016}}</ref> He is also the brother of actress [[Suchitra Murali]].\n\n==Filmography==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" \n|-\n!No !! Year !! Film !! Role !!Cast || Notes\n|-\n|1|| 2008|| ''[[Crazy Gopalan]]'' || Director<br>Writer ||[[Dileep (actor)|Dileep]], [[Saleem Kumar]], [[Manoj K. Jayan]], Radha Varma ||\n|-\n|2|| 2009 || ''[[Winter (2009 film)|Winter]]'' || Director || [[Jayaram]], [[Bhavana (actress)|Bhavana]] ||\n|-\n|3|| 2011