-all}}</ref>\n*  1975   &ndash; [[Erik Ohlsson (musician)|Erik Ohlsson]], Swedish singer and guitarist \n*  1975   &ndash; [[Stefan Terblanche]], South African rugby player\n*[[1976]] &ndash; [[Kriszti\u00e1n Lisztes]], Hungarian footballer\n*  1976   &ndash; [[Tom\u00e1\u0161 Vokoun]], Czech-American ice hockey player\n*[[1977]] &ndash; [[Deniz Bar\u0131\u015f]], Turkish footballer\n*[[1978]] &ndash; [[J\u00fcri Ratas]], Estonian politician, 42nd [[Mayor of Tallinn]]\n*[[1979]] &ndash; [[Walter Davis (triple jumper)|Walter Davis]], American triple jumper\n* 1979    &ndash; [[Ahmed al-Ghamdi]], Saudi Arabian terrorist, hijacker of [[United Airlines Flight 175]] (d. 2001)\n*  1979   &ndash; [[Sam Hornish Jr.]], American race car driver\n*  1979   &ndash; [[Joe Thornton]], Canadian ice hockey player\n*[[1980]] &ndash; [[Nyjer Morgan]], American baseball player\n*[[1981]] &ndash; [[Nathan Ellington]], English footballer \n*  1981   &ndash; [[Carlos Rogers (American football)|Carlos Rogers]], American football player\n*[[1983]] &ndash; [[Michelle Branch]], American singer-songwriter and guitarist\n*  1983   &ndash; [[Kyle Hogg]], English cricketer\n*[[1984]] &ndash; [[Thomas Kortegaard]], Danish footballer\n*  1984   &ndash; [[Johnny Weir]], American figure skater\n*[[1985]] &ndash; [[Rhett Bomar]], American football player\n*  1985   &ndash; [[Chad Henne]], American football player\n*  1985   &ndash; [[Ashley Tisdale]], American actress, singer, and producer <ref>https://www.allmusic.com/artist/ashley-tisdale-mn0000469519</ref>\n*[[1986]] &ndash; [[Brett Cecil]], American baseball player\n*  1986   &ndash; [[Lindsay Lohan]], American actress and singer<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/10536573|work=BBC|title=Lindsay Lohan's chequered life in the spotlight|date=July 7, 2010|accessdate=December 28, 2016}}</ref>\n*[[1987]] &ndash; [[Esteban Granero]], Spanish footballer\n*[[1988]] &ndash; [[Lee Chung-yong]], South Korean footballer\n*[[1989]] &ndash; [[Nadezhda